[
  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Ellicott's Commentary for English Readers",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(28) ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "For thou wilt.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—Better, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Thou makest bright my lamp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In Samuel, “It is thou Jehovah who art my lamp.” This obvious metaphor is common in Hebrew, as in all literature. Light is an emblem of prosperity, happiness, or life itself. (Comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Job 18:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Job 21:17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Proverbs 13:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", &c). It happens to be used very frequently of David and his family (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1Kings 11:36",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1Kings 15:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2Kings 8:19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
